node.text: What a great day. Unbelievable vibes. I love that little turkey more than anything in the whole world. She put so much time & effort into the planning of our big day. Happy & blessed. I’ll have the whole video soon, not really sure about posting it yet, but I’ll keep y’all updated. P&L
